==Italian==

===Etymology===
From an old compound, whose constituents are ''que-'' (see [[ecco]]) and Latin ''istum'', neuter of the pronoun [[iste]]

===Adjective===
'''questo''' {{m}} ({{f}} questa, {{m}} {{plural}} questi, {{f}} {{p}} queste)

# [[this]], [[these]]

===Pronoun===
'''questo''' {{m}} ({{f}} questa, {{m}} {{plural}} questi, {{f}} {{plural}} queste)

# this one, these ones

===Usage notes===
* Quest' in the singular, before a vowel

